metadata.name: 5Tars NFT Super Pack
metadata.description: The 5TARS NFT Super pack contains 2 random albums, 14 random cards (football players, managers and teams) and 2 Power Cards (exclusive for this pack). 5tars.io is a revolutionary football prediction gaming platform. The pack also offers a 35% discount in the in-game shop, and the Power Cards act as boosters to earn more points in the Arenas.
